short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirect search queries to other search engines

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
G-Classic gives users the power to diversify their search results. With just two clicks, users can check their search terms on various search engines including Google, Bing, Yahoo!, and DuckDuckGo. 

Developed by: Ben Acheff, Zackary Lee, and Eric Yager
